title: Sealed with a Kiss by Jill Monroe. PDF (Perseu)
description:
Thanks to her distracted sister, hotel owner Rachel
Sutherland is now alone to greet berhot Navy SEAL
Riley Wilkes as he disembarks. But when Riley scoops
Rachel into his arms for a hot, combustible kiss,
Rachel wonders if she owes her sister a big favor....
Now Rachel is reconsidering her stance on bad boys...
especially those of the Riley Wilkes variety. In fact,
a naughty little fling could be just what the doctor
ordered. Because the only thing better than a SEAL
in his uniform, is a SEAL out of his uniform....

Sealed with a Kiss
By: Jill Monroe
